{
  "stem": "214.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then one day, they came and they said that I should take the train to Warsaw and pick up the contract from this man.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they told me his name and said, when I get off the-- well-- the train depot, the main train depot in [NON-ENGLISH], he looks so and so.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would him how I look, and OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you weren't taking the train into the ghetto, the Umschlagplatz, you were--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no platz yet in Warsaw, see-- there was no ghetto yet in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was 1940.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The ghetto was not closed yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't come from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was coming from-- I was coming from Skierniewice, see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was going to Warsaw now not as a Jew-- to meet this Pole.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was going to Warsaw as a Pole.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I came-- it was maybe 5 o'clock in the afternoon, I do not remember anymore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, this is another thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know-- furs, wearing a fur, was absolutely also punishable by death.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was this action before in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, this kind of-- I mean, we were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, so I-- but-- it was winter, and Poland is cold.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I must have, my mother-- it wasn't even expensive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's was, what do you call the seal skins?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Seal skins?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Which was, I think, one of the cheapest furs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I-- I took my mother's coat, and anyway, here I get off the-- the train and meet this gentleman, and he's very courteous, and very-- I mean, he treat me like-- you know-- I don't know what he-- and he says, well, I think before we do anything with the papers, let's go and have some dinner.",
      "word_count": 58
    }
  ],
